`A⁻¹ A = I` implies `A A⁻¹ = I` as a matrix equality. -/
theorem higham9_15_matrix_right_inverse_of_matrix_left_inverse {n : ℕ}
    (A Ainv : Matrix (Fin n) (Fin n) ℝ)
