growth value satisfies Wilkinson's elementary `2^(n-1)` bound. -/
theorem higham9_partialPivotingUTraceGrowthValues_le_pow_two {n : ℕ} {r : ℝ}
    (hr : r ∈ higham9_partialPivotingUTraceGrowthValues n) :
    r ≤ (2 : ℝ) ^ (n - 1) := by
