/-- **Theorem 9.7 / equation (9.10)**, source-shaped supremum form of
Wilkinson's exact GEPP growth bound for recursive partial-pivoting `U` traces. -/
theorem higham9_7_partialPivotingUTraceGrowthSup_le_pow_two {n : ℕ}
